window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>What's a man to do when a gorgeous redhead walks into his office with an offer to find El Dorado? Get on the next plane to Peru. </b> </p> <p>Vic Wilde's gotten in more than a little trouble for operating outside the lines when it comes to hunting ancient treasure. But when he discovers that the clandestine Order of the Golden Dawn is looking for the Lost City, he knows he has to find it first. </p> <p>And he has the perfect team to help him do it. </p> <p>A fiery Brit who's quick with a pistol, and even quicker with her sharp tongue. </p> <p>An adorable blonde grad student with perfect curves and a willingness to learn. </p> <p>And a mysterious figure with golden eyes, watching from the shadows. </p> <p>Vic will do whatever it takes to find El Dorado, braving the deepest and most remote parts of the Amazon. But will he be able to beat the Golden Dawn to the treasure? Or will he lose himself in the bodies of his seductive companions? </p> <p><b><i>Wild Gold</i></b><b> is an adventure fantasy for men featuring beautiful women, a clever hero, and plenty of action and adventure.</b></p>"; 
